productReviews.reviewText: one of my hobbies is scuba diving. and when i'm scuba diving this works great.
My co-worker Merwin has one of these. He says it looks bubbly.
My neighbor Fannie has one of these. She works as a teacher and she says it looks spiky.
The box this comes in is 3 inch by 6 centimeter and weights 15 ounce!
I saw one of these in Vanuatu and I bought one.
